      Key to entities used below:
      &#x05D0; - The Hebrew letter Alef (strongly RTL).
      &#x05D1; - The Hebrew letter Bet (strongly RTL).
      &#x05D2; - The Hebrew letter Gimel (strongly RTL).
    </div></head><div class="comments">
